{ /* Perform any hardware setup necessary. */ prvSetupHardware(); /* --- APPLICATION TASKS CAN BE CREATED HERE --- */ /* Start the created tasks running. */ vTaskStartScheduler(); /* Execution will only reach here if there was insufficient heap to start the scheduler. */ for( ;; ); return 0;
} Listing 2.1 The template for a new main() function

